A '''bombing run''' was a tactic used by many factions throughout history, wherein a bomber craft&mdash;such as a [[TIE/sa tactical bomber/Legends|TIE/sa bomber]], [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|BTL Y-wing starfighter]], or [[GAT-12 Skipray Blastboat]]&mdash;would lay a load of bombs across a large surface area. Despite being devastating against closely-grouped enemies, a bombing run could be thwarted by well-placed anti-aircraft defenses.

